1
00:00:17,333 --> 00:00:18,160
Aunt,

2
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:20,239
have a sip of tea and take your time.

3
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:23,359
Three years ago,

4
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,760
your eldest cousin
trusted the wrong people.

5
00:00:25,984 --> 00:00:27,640
He couldn't refuse them
out of politeness

6
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:29,480
and was forced

7
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,719
to ghostwrite that essay.

8
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,600
Now, it's been dug up.

9
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:34,799
You know

10
00:00:35,759 --> 00:00:38,000
your grandfather is strictly principled.

11
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:40,200
He definitely won't step forward
to plead for him.

12
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:44,119
Your uncle is furious,

13
00:00:44,359 --> 00:00:45,719
but he has no other way either.

14
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,200
Xihe,

15
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:51,000
I am truly at my wits' end.

16
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,000
That's why I've come to beg you.

17
00:00:56,624 --> 00:00:58,720
Your Highness, I urge you
to consider carefully.

18
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,079
There are three thousand candidates
this year.

19
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:04,200
If, as you said, we
investigate this to the very end,

20
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,200
I'm afraid

21
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:07,120
half of the noble families

22
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,079
will be wearing mourning clothes.

23
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:09,840
Your Highness,

24
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:12,719
the Censorate executed
twenty-seven people in seven days,

25
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:14,200
causing a mutiny in the border army.

26
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,879
Furthermore, corrupt officials
are using the fraud case

27
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,239
to frame the loyal and good.

28
00:01:18,239 --> 00:01:20,840
I am not afraid of cutting out the sore,

29
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:23,680
but of damaging the heart
and lungs in the process.

30
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:29,599
We are willing to risk our lives
to guarantee a thorough investigation,

31
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:32,439
but please make it clear, Your Highness.

32
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,920
If the case reaches the Censorate

33
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:37,879
and a prince's disciple passes a note,
what should be done?

34
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:41,599
Can this executioner's blade
sever a golden chain?

35
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:46,288
Harsh laws for urgent times,
gentle handling for delicate matters.

36
00:01:46,336 --> 00:01:47,640
Your Highness, it might be better

37
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:50,439
to first execute
the seven confirmed corrupt officials

38
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:52,000
to uphold the law,

39
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:55,359
and as for the other involved scholars,

40
00:01:55,424 --> 00:01:57,430
(Sixian Hall)
send them to serve in the military.

41
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,439
This fulfills your goal
of purging the selection process,

42
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:05,280
while avoiding the risk
of alienating the noble families.

43
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,680
Great.

44
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:13,800
What a perfectly safe piece of advice.

45
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,240
Do you all know

46
00:02:15,968 --> 00:02:17,430
how many innocent souls are buried

47
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,680
in the fraud cases of past dynasties?

48
00:02:20,128 --> 00:02:22,800
The bribes in this year's examination
are piled to the ceiling.

49
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,039
Even the children
in the streets are singing,

50
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:28,280
"The rich claim the golden list,
while the poor bury their ink."

51
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,919
My father implemented
the talent selection system

52
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,840
to break

53
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:35,552
the noble families' monopoly
on officialdom,

54
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,520
giving students
from humble backgrounds a chance

55
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:39,330
to realize their ambitions
and showcase their talents.

56
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:41,350
Now, this buying and selling
of examination results

57
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,070
is crueler than the harsh officials
in the Discourses on Salt and Iron.

58
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,479
Poor scholars

59
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:48,719
pour their hearts out
and study hard for a decade,

60
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,840
only to end up as ghostwriters
for the rich.

61
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:54,000
I'll lay it on the line today.

62
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,639
Anyone involved
in this examination fraud,

63
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,960
from nobles down to petty clerks,

64
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:00,120
every single one of them

65
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,280
will not be spared.

66
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:04,199
Your Highness,

67
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:09,000
Commandery Princess Zhaoning's cousin,

68
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:11,280
Minister Tao's eldest grandson,

69
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,080
was also involved in the fraud.

70
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,199
The evidence is conclusive.

71
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:37,008
=Blossoms of Power=

72
00:04:37,008 --> 00:04:40,300
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

73
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:43,020
=Episode 20=

74
00:04:43,780 --> 00:04:45,750
(East Palace)

75
00:04:46,048 --> 00:04:47,830
Xihe, you came to see me
on your own accord.

76
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:49,120
I assume regarding your cousin,

77
00:04:49,504 --> 00:04:51,160
your aunt has already pleaded with you.

78
00:04:51,536 --> 00:04:53,312
You guessed correctly, Your Highness.

79
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,360
Xihe, I...

80
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,879
You don't need to say anything.

81
00:04:57,296 --> 00:04:58,930
There's no need to show him favoritism.

82
00:04:58,959 --> 00:05:00,279
Since my cousin made a mistake,

83
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:02,639
he should be dealt with accordingly.

84
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,432
People must always pay the price

85
00:05:04,464 --> 00:05:05,720
for the mistakes they make.

86
00:05:05,824 --> 00:05:07,350
Only then can they learn their lesson

87
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,439
and hold reverence for the law.

88
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,312
Then what about
your grandfather's family?

89
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,879
How do you consider them?

90
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,160
My grandfather is not at fault.

91
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,800
No one can use this
to falsely accuse him.

92
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:20,560
As for whether my aunt
will hold a grudge against me,

93
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:22,680
that is not my concern.

94
00:05:22,912 --> 00:05:24,070
I have a clear conscience.

95
00:05:28,784 --> 00:05:30,510
Why are you looking at me like that?

96
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,839
Along this journey,

97
00:05:32,704 --> 00:05:35,140
you clearly need the support
of your maternal family the most,

98
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,959
yet you risk offending the Tao family

99
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,740
to place righteousness
above family loyalty.

100
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,519
I can see that

101
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,319
you're looking forward to

102
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,879
a peaceful and prosperous nation.

103
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:49,000
Qingzhi once sent me a policy essay.

104
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,560
Its insights were unique
and its arguments sweeping.

105
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,279
The essay began by stating,

106
00:05:53,328 --> 00:05:55,070
"I have heard
that the essence of governance

107
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,912
lies in equitable land distribution
and the people's peace.

108
00:05:56,944 --> 00:05:59,840
The teachings on regulating water
and land are still fresh in our minds.

109
00:05:59,872 --> 00:06:01,560
Yet today, all fertile land
belongs to the wealthy,

110
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,940
while the poor have not even
a sliver of land to stand on."

111
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,439
You remember it word for word.

112
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,600
The writing was so bold,

113
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,040
and it's truly unforgettable.

114
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,160
Back then, my only thought

115
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:17,040
was to catch the person who poisoned me.

116
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,759
Over time,

117
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:20,920
my heart filled with resentment
and bitterness.

118
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,279
The master at the Taoist temple
suggested I travel.

119
00:06:24,656 --> 00:06:26,368
Taking the imperial examination
at the time

120
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:27,344
was just a whim.

121
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,680
But I saw with my own eyes

122
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:34,270
candidates getting the exam questions
in advance

123
00:06:34,592 --> 00:06:36,240
and swapping their papers on the spot,

124
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:40,079
while the examiners turned a blind eye.

125
00:06:41,904 --> 00:06:43,870
I could have submitted a memorial
to the throne,

126
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:45,160
but I knew

127
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,879
even if I reported it then,

128
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,040
it would only clean up
the local practices temporarily.

129
00:06:49,088 --> 00:06:50,944
It wouldn't serve
as a nationwide deterrent.

130
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,839
What I want

131
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,439
is a sweeping and decisive purge.

132
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,040
For at least ten years,

133
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,920
I want wrongdoers

134
00:06:58,928 --> 00:07:00,680
not to even dare harbor evil thoughts,

135
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,144
and allow those with true ambition

136
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,199
to stand out.

137
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,879
Your time among the people back then

138
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:08,040
is what makes you so clear-headed
and thorough today.

139
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,959
But regarding this matter,

140
00:07:10,839 --> 00:07:12,240
how did you know it was me?

141
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,879
I remember

142
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:16,399
the candidate they later investigated

143
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,639
was named Xiao Huaiqian.

144
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,040
Xiao and Xiao sound the same.

145
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,720
Hua was changed to Huai,

146
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,759
turning outward brilliance
into inner depth.

147
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,720
Yong was changed to Qian,

148
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,279
turning noble arrogance
into a humble demeanor.

149
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,199
It showed that the person

150
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:35,160
wanted to hide his prominent identity.

151
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,839
No matter how I disguise myself,

152
00:07:38,416 --> 00:07:39,950
you can always see right through it.

153
00:07:41,519 --> 00:07:42,959
Just like when we first met.

154
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:46,399
I also know that

155
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:49,600
while catching
the poisoner is important,

156
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,800
what you never forget

157
00:07:52,144 --> 00:07:53,488
is eliminating the chronic poison

158
00:07:53,520 --> 00:07:55,430
that has seeped into the nation's veins.

159
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,160
So regarding my cousin,

160
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,279
you need not worry.

161
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:00,720
Please enforce the law impartially
and set an example.

162
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,000
Now that we've discussed everything,

163
00:08:07,056 --> 00:08:08,390
I should head back to the manor.

164
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,312
Before you go back,

165
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:12,120
I'd like to take you somewhere.

166
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,079
Come.

167
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,680
Here are your meatballs.

168
00:08:22,759 --> 00:08:23,759
Enjoy your meal.

169
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:40,480
If others saw you right now,

170
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,000
who would think

171
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,670
you're the cold and heartless
Commandery Princess Zhaoning?

172
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:47,519
If you could see yourself right now,

173
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,360
you wouldn't think

174
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:51,159
you're the calculating

175
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,559
and deeply scheming Crown Prince.

176
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,000
Slow down.

177
00:09:27,279 --> 00:09:28,200
You two,

178
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,919
come in and guess some riddles!

179
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:32,980
(A Lady Holding Up the Roof
Stabilizes the World)

180
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:36,039
Do you know the answer?

181
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:39,159
A roof radical over a lady

182
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,030
combined with the character for "lady"

183
00:09:41,072 --> 00:09:42,640
makes the character "An" for peace.

184
00:09:42,704 --> 00:09:45,300
(Peace)

185
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,200
It's a good riddle.

186
00:09:47,264 --> 00:09:48,480
For the world to be at peace,

187
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,600
ladies should
naturally have their place.

188
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,960
This riddle is quite unique.

189
00:10:01,088 --> 00:10:03,360
The bottom of "Qin"
is the character "He" for grain.

190
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,159
Grain is wood, and water nurtures wood.

191
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,992
Replacing it with water makes
the character "Tai" for prosperity.

192
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,279
Only with abundant agriculture

193
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,416
can the country prosper
and the people be at peace.

194
00:10:11,216 --> 00:10:12,440
(National Prosperity and Peace)

195
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,360
Though I've long known
of your unmatched brilliance,

196
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,120
every single time,

197
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:21,120
you still manage to amaze me.

198
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,799
It's the riddle maker
who hid the foundation of the state

199
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,799
within the strokes of the characters.

200
00:10:25,856 --> 00:10:27,150
It's the foundation of the state

201
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,639
hidden in your heart.

202
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,559
Would you care

203
00:10:40,608 --> 00:10:42,720
to add a token of good fortune
to the blessing?

204
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,240
In the royal court,

205
00:10:51,296 --> 00:10:53,472
I only wish for peace
and prosperity for the nation.

206
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,720
But when I am with you,

207
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,790
I only pray for our twin lotuses
to bloom.

208
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,320
It's beautiful.

209
00:12:09,472 --> 00:12:11,240
The night is late and the dew is heavy.

210
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:13,279
Couldn't I take care of it for you?

211
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:15,559
Why must you trouble yourself?

212
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:17,120
If you catch a cold,

213
00:12:17,130 --> 00:12:18,830
you'll have to drink
herbal medicine again.

214
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,080
This flower is delicate.

215
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:23,000
It will wither
if not carefully tended to.

216
00:12:23,728 --> 00:12:25,728
I wouldn't feel at ease
leaving it to others.

217
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,200
Mo Yu,

218
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,900
go fetch some more hot spring water.

219
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,399
Yes.

220
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:50,799
The reason this Slender-Leaf Qionghua
is so precious

221
00:12:50,799 --> 00:12:52,320
is that it can be used in medicine.

222
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:54,600
It nourishes the yin,
protects the lungs, and detoxifies.

223
00:12:54,759 --> 00:12:56,679
The Crown Prince coughs frequently.

224
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,430
Half of it is a disguise
in front of others,

225
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,879
and half of it is real.

226
00:13:00,016 --> 00:13:03,100
I'm afraid the residual poison hasn't
been cleared and has damaged his lungs.

227
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:06,879
So Her Highness works so hard

228
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,440
all for the Crown Prince.

229
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,000
Could this be

230
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,080
what the storybooks call

231
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:16,679
"the dawn of love
and deep-rooted affection"?

232
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:20,060
(Residence of the Heir
of the Marquis of Shunan)

233
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,039
Hurry up.

234
00:13:22,039 --> 00:13:22,759
Handle with care.

235
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:23,799
Got it.

236
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,399
That Cui Jinbai.

237
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,879
I haven't seen him for days.

238
00:13:30,928 --> 00:13:33,120
He's been busy with Crown Prince
on the fraud case.

239
00:13:33,136 --> 00:13:34,680
I thought he had let me off the hook.

240
00:13:50,032 --> 00:13:51,504
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

241
00:13:53,344 --> 00:13:55,200
Look at how carefully
he's picking things out.

242
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:56,480
Anyone who didn't know

243
00:13:56,592 --> 00:13:59,120
would think he's planning
to live here for thirty years.

244
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:01,840
Halt.

245
00:14:04,639 --> 00:14:05,240
What is it?

246
00:14:05,344 --> 00:14:06,270
Where are you going?

247
00:14:07,056 --> 00:14:08,320
Just going out for a stroll.

248
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:08,992
I'll go with you.

249
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,480
No need.

250
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,600
I suddenly feel

251
00:14:14,039 --> 00:14:15,200
a bit tired.

252
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:17,399
I'll go back and rest.

253
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:17,799
Alright.

254
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:21,296
I have some business
at the Court of Judicial Review later.

255
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:22,399
Get some good rest.

256
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:25,440
Okay.

257
00:14:25,536 --> 00:14:26,480
You go do your thing.

258
00:14:26,480 --> 00:14:27,320
I won't bother you.

259
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:27,759
See you.

260
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:37,600
Young Master Bu,

261
00:14:37,679 --> 00:14:39,559
you haven't been here for days.

262
00:14:39,559 --> 00:14:41,200
It's not that I didn't want to come.

263
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,559
During the fraud case,

264
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:44,960
I had to keep a close eye
on the security of the capital.

265
00:14:48,799 --> 00:14:49,519
Yu'er,

266
00:14:49,584 --> 00:14:51,750
your little hands are getting
even softer and whiter.

267
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,399
Come.

268
00:14:54,688 --> 00:14:56,840
Young Master Bu,
you're lingering among the beauties,

269
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,159
looking quite delighted.

270
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,440
Why are you here?

271
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:02,368
You're playing around
with official courtesans.

272
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:04,380
Do you know you've committed
the crime of corruption?

273
00:15:04,399 --> 00:15:05,559
Stop talking nonsense.

274
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,919
Don't think because you're
in the Court of Judicial Review

275
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:07,639
and have been a Vice Minister
for a few years,

276
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:08,976
you can just pin crimes on people.

277
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,500
In our dynasty, official courtesans
are performing artists

278
00:15:10,519 --> 00:15:11,650
belonging to the government.

279
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:12,799
According to the law,

280
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:15,200
officials who are overly intimate
with official courtesans

281
00:15:15,216 --> 00:15:16,630
face ten years in prison.

282
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:24,360
I was just looking
at Yu'er's soft white hands

283
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,559
and joking around a bit.

284
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,030
It seems you know you're in the wrong.

285
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:30,200
I can let this matter go for now,

286
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,440
but you must promise me

287
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,600
never to set foot
in these pleasure houses again.

288
00:15:37,568 --> 00:15:40,240
What gives you the right to deprive me
of my right to enjoy myself?

289
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,830
Are you that inseparable
from singing and dancing?

290
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,679
Yes. You don't know
how to appreciate it,

291
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:44,759
and you want to stop others
from appreciating it too.

292
00:15:44,759 --> 00:15:45,840
You're simply unreasonable.

293
00:15:47,039 --> 00:15:47,480
Fine.

294
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,320
I'll accompany you.

295
00:15:51,759 --> 00:15:53,120
He's accompanying you?

296
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:54,720
Suit yourself.

297
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,759
Do you know what dance this is?

298
00:16:07,759 --> 00:16:09,120
Isn't it just a water sleeve dance?

299
00:16:11,399 --> 00:16:12,759
This is the Qingshang dance.

300
00:16:12,832 --> 00:16:14,440
It originates
from the Han Dynasty Music Bureau.

301
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,690
Specifically, the three Qingshang modes
of Xianghe songs.

302
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:19,120
It features rare dances
and extraordinary talents.

303
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:22,144
Several emperors of the
previous dynasties loved this dance.

304
00:16:22,192 --> 00:16:24,540
Later, it became widely popular
among the common people.

305
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:27,620
The Music Office continuously absorbed
and improved upon folk music and dance,

306
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:30,000
resulting in the spectacular performance
we see today.

307
00:16:34,879 --> 00:16:35,639
You may step down.

308
00:16:45,344 --> 00:16:47,670
Qian'er's pipa playing,
in the entire imperial capital,

309
00:16:47,879 --> 00:16:49,480
can be considered unparalleled.

310
00:16:51,399 --> 00:16:54,080
Then tell me, this piece,
White Snow in Spring Sunlight,

311
00:16:54,256 --> 00:16:55,824
what makes it so unparalleled?

312
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:02,500
Spring Sunlight is derived
from all things sensing the spring,

313
00:17:02,519 --> 00:17:03,840
and the gentle, soothing breeze.

314
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:05,160
White Snow

315
00:17:05,599 --> 00:17:07,079
is derived from awe-inspiring purity,

316
00:17:07,080 --> 00:17:08,672
and the crisp sound of snow on bamboo.

317
00:17:08,704 --> 00:17:10,590
Her playing technique
is beautiful and fluent.

318
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,319
But it's too beautiful,

319
00:17:12,512 --> 00:17:14,550
thus losing the original intention
of this piece.

320
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,160
Decadent music

321
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:18,079
is truly inferior.

322
00:17:22,272 --> 00:17:23,110
Young Master Bu,

323
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:24,359
do you know...

324
00:17:29,079 --> 00:17:31,680
- Young Master!
- Young Master!

325
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,790
What's wrong, Young Master?

326
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:40,830
Are you feeling unwell?

327
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:41,750
My head hurts.

328
00:17:42,310 --> 00:17:43,400
Go bring

329
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,070
Xie Yunhuai here.

330
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,480
You may have caught a cold.

331
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:47,510
I'll go get your medicine.

332
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,240
Have you forgotten?

333
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,780
Physician Xie
has gone beyond the frontier.

334
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,720
Forget it.

335
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:58,550
This is infuriating.

336
00:17:58,830 --> 00:17:59,680
Young Master Bu,

337
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:02,200
where are you feeling unwell?

338
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,960
What are you doing here?

339
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:08,550
Don't you go to
the Court of Judicial Review?

340
00:18:09,250 --> 00:18:11,580
Is this how the Young Master's Residence
treats its guests?

341
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,830
Won't you even offer me a seat?

342
00:18:14,420 --> 00:18:15,960
Do you really not want
to see me that much?

343
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:16,750
What do you think?

344
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:18,070
Every single day,

345
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,200
you keep an eye on me
from morning till night.

346
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,990
One of these days,
you're going to drive me crazy.

347
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:24,000
If you could keep yourself in check,

348
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:25,160
I wouldn't have to.

349
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:28,160
Why should I?

350
00:18:28,210 --> 00:18:30,240
I've lived freely in the imperial capital
since I was a child.

351
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:31,200
No one has ever tried
to keep me in line.

352
00:18:31,210 --> 00:18:33,000
I've long been used to
living without restraints.

353
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,510
If you can't stand it, then move out.

354
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:35,510
It suits us both.

355
00:18:39,910 --> 00:18:41,030
You're not leaving, are you?

356
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:43,310
Fine. I'll go.

357
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:56,680
Young Master.

358
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,640
Although Physician Xie isn't here,

359
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,470
a highly skilled foreign physician
has just arrived.

360
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,830
I'll go invite him over.

361
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,000
Get out.

362
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,720
Just get out.

363
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:34,510
Why are you sitting here?

364
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:35,510
Waiting for you to calm down.

365
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,680
Calm down?

366
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,830
The moment I see you, I can't calm down.

367
00:19:40,310 --> 00:19:41,310
Then don't look at me.

368
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,000
Lord Cui,

369
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:54,480
I'm begging you.

370
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,750
Will you just leave me alone?

371
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,110
Fine.

372
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,110
I promise.

373
00:20:00,210 --> 00:20:02,160
From now on, I'll try not to go
to those places so often.

374
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:02,550
Good.

375
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,400
But if you break your word,

376
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,750
I'll do what I did today again.

377
00:20:24,980 --> 00:20:27,300
(East Palace)

378
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:28,360
Your Highness.

379
00:20:29,490 --> 00:20:31,280
This time, I traveled
far beyond the borders

380
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,090
and brought back
an extraordinary person.

381
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:34,950
He is especially skilled
in detoxification.

382
00:20:34,990 --> 00:20:35,750
I took the liberty

383
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,910
of having him diagnose you,
Your Highness.

384
00:20:38,190 --> 00:20:40,430
Greetings, Your Highness.

385
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,370
Then I will trouble you, Physician Ale.

386
00:21:03,990 --> 00:21:05,350
How could His Highness's blood

387
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,640
be like this?

388
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,520
Tell me,

389
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,560
how much time do I have left?

390
00:21:24,710 --> 00:21:26,280
Originally, you had three to five years.

391
00:21:27,080 --> 00:21:28,040
But Your Highness,

392
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:31,120
you've risked your life several times
and damaged your meridians.

393
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:32,600
Now,

394
00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:36,190
you only have one year left.

395
00:21:50,150 --> 00:21:51,560
Is it truly beyond saving?

396
00:21:54,280 --> 00:21:55,670
There is one more method.

397
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,900
This set of golden needles

398
00:21:59,030 --> 00:22:01,800
has been soaked in a poison-drawing
decoction Ale specially formulated.

399
00:22:01,860 --> 00:22:04,390
They can be inserted into acupoints
to fight poison with poison.

400
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:05,470
However, this method,

401
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:07,280
compared to previous treatments,

402
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,950
will be a hundred times more painful.

403
00:22:09,120 --> 00:22:10,280
A hundred times more painful?

404
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:12,430
The previous poison treatments

405
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:14,660
were as painful
as scraping bone and piercing the heart.

406
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:16,390
How can His Highness endure this?

407
00:22:16,800 --> 00:22:17,670
Speak freely.

408
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:19,990
There are twelve needles in total.

409
00:22:20,320 --> 00:22:21,670
Three needles break mortal bones.

410
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:25,040
Twelve needles shatter the soul.

411
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,670
By the eighth needle,

412
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:29,080
even the toughest man

413
00:22:29,490 --> 00:22:31,890
will be in so much pain
that his soul will shatter.

414
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:37,880
You've experienced it yourself?

415
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:40,640
Let me see.

416
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,520
I am incompetent.

417
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:52,290
I could only endure four needles.

418
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:54,710
Why did you go to such lengths?

419
00:22:58,390 --> 00:22:59,670
You secured a title of honor

420
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:01,670
for my mother.

421
00:23:01,990 --> 00:23:04,120
Your kindness to me
is as deep as the sea.

422
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,360
Even if my body is smashed to pieces,

423
00:23:06,950 --> 00:23:08,280
I am willing to do it.

424
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:15,840
We will use this method.

425
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,750
Whenever I think of her,

426
00:23:24,950 --> 00:23:25,950
I know I cannot die.

427
00:23:28,360 --> 00:23:29,990
As long as I can stay by her side,

428
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:33,150
even one more day is good.

429
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:58,360
Your Highness, why did you summon me

430
00:23:58,360 --> 00:23:59,190
to the palace?

431
00:23:59,430 --> 00:24:00,600
I've seen Yunhuai.

432
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:03,040
He told me some good news.

433
00:24:03,670 --> 00:24:04,670
What good news?

434
00:24:07,390 --> 00:24:08,390
Yunhuai said

435
00:24:08,950 --> 00:24:09,840
right now,

436
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:12,230
I don't even have three
to five years left.

437
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:14,910
That's good news?

438
00:24:16,900 --> 00:24:19,010
You won't have to keep your guard up
against me.

439
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:20,470
Isn't that good news?

440
00:24:27,910 --> 00:24:29,230
How much time is left?

441
00:24:32,190 --> 00:24:32,800
One year.

442
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,390
This might not be a bad thing.

443
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:50,320
After all, what you valued in me
from the start

444
00:24:50,670 --> 00:24:51,520
was my short life.

445
00:24:55,750 --> 00:24:57,080
Why don't we make a deal?

446
00:24:59,080 --> 00:24:59,910
What deal?

447
00:25:00,430 --> 00:25:01,670
My lifelong wish

448
00:25:02,470 --> 00:25:03,430
is to marry you.

449
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:05,040
If you are willing to marry me,

450
00:25:05,470 --> 00:25:06,750
I will form an alliance with you,

451
00:25:07,140 --> 00:25:09,600
and help you keep the Shen family
and the Northwest Army safe.

452
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:10,640
Everything you want,

453
00:25:11,230 --> 00:25:12,430
I will give to you.

454
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:14,390
You believe
that people's hearts are fickle.

455
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:17,040
Even if I were to have a change of heart
after we marry,

456
00:25:17,170 --> 00:25:19,150
I wouldn't live long enough
to be your enemy.

457
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,560
If you become the Crown Princess,

458
00:25:21,670 --> 00:25:23,220
it will make things much easier for you.

459
00:25:23,560 --> 00:25:25,710
You can also help me fulfill
my unfulfilled wishes.

460
00:25:28,230 --> 00:25:29,430
Your wish

461
00:25:29,910 --> 00:25:31,470
is to find the one who poisoned you?

462
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:34,360
It used to be.

463
00:25:35,320 --> 00:25:36,230
Now,

464
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:38,390
not entirely.

465
00:25:41,990 --> 00:25:43,040
This poison

466
00:25:43,630 --> 00:25:45,800
should not become a curse
that traps me.

467
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:48,520
No matter how much time
heaven grants me,

468
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:51,360
I should do more

469
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,150
meaningful things for the world.

470
00:25:59,090 --> 00:26:01,300
These are the dates chosen
by the Ministry of Rites.

471
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:04,290
If you are willing
to join hands with me,

472
00:26:04,390 --> 00:26:05,280
then pick one.

473
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,360
But don't pick one too far
in the future.

474
00:26:13,410 --> 00:26:15,040
I'm afraid I won't live to see it.

475
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,430
As for your words today,

476
00:26:34,430 --> 00:26:35,640
I will consider them carefully.

477
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:38,080
Xihe,

478
00:26:39,120 --> 00:26:40,470
every word you say,

479
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,520
every single syllable,

480
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,430
I will keep firmly in my heart.

481
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:51,390
If you want to say something
that will break my heart,

482
00:26:53,670 --> 00:26:54,880
don't say it lightly.

483
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:07,060
(Auspicious Day for Marriage: 10th Day
of the 2nd Month, 23rd Year of Youning)

484
00:27:07,060 --> 00:27:09,420
(Auspicious Day for Marriage: 2nd Day
of the 3rd Month, 23rd Year of Youning)

485
00:27:09,420 --> 00:27:11,300
(Auspicious Day for Marriage: 8th Day
of the 5th Month, 23rd Year of Youning)

486
00:27:22,900 --> 00:27:25,340
♪A wall that collapses at a single push♪

487
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:28,940
♪Frost that melts at a single smile♪

488
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:35,100
♪How can you be this wonderful♪

489
00:27:37,180 --> 00:27:39,980
♪I've hidden so many words♪

490
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:43,380
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

491
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:51,540
♪So never uncover♪

492
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:54,220
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

493
00:27:54,580 --> 00:27:57,620
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

494
00:27:58,640 --> 00:27:59,950
I was picking Immortal Vine,

495
00:28:00,370 --> 00:28:01,520
and happened to save you.

496
00:28:03,230 --> 00:28:04,280
Save me...

497
00:28:05,390 --> 00:28:06,670
That was our first encounter.

498
00:28:07,250 --> 00:28:09,120
There was absolutely
no scheming involved.

499
00:28:11,910 --> 00:28:13,280
But as long as you believe

500
00:28:14,360 --> 00:28:16,080
that I will never hurt you,

501
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,470
that is enough.

502
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,800
Do you know

503
00:28:21,830 --> 00:28:23,560
why it withers once it leaves the water?

504
00:28:24,990 --> 00:28:26,040
Because it was born

505
00:28:26,950 --> 00:28:28,750
to be bathed in the gaze of lovers.

506
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:33,840
Do you know

507
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:35,800
how much I wanted you to ask,

508
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:38,360
"Where are you going?"

509
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:40,400
"What are you going to do?"

510
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:44,700
♪Give you a moon in return♪

511
00:28:45,950 --> 00:28:46,950
Since I was nine,

512
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,560
I haven't known what joy is.

513
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:52,190
But now,

514
00:28:53,750 --> 00:28:54,560
I know.

515
00:28:56,190 --> 00:28:57,470
It is being with you.

516
00:28:58,040 --> 00:28:59,390
I'm very easy to coax.

517
00:29:00,430 --> 00:29:01,560
Even if it's a lie,

518
00:29:02,190 --> 00:29:03,320
I'm willing to believe it.

519
00:29:04,670 --> 00:29:06,120
I wonder if you would be willing

520
00:29:07,080 --> 00:29:07,800
to marry me.

521
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:13,500
♪You'll never♪

522
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:23,220
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

523
00:29:42,740 --> 00:29:45,140
♪Wind that misses the grasp♪

524
00:29:46,180 --> 00:29:48,660
♪Light that ignites at a single touch♪

525
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:54,900
♪A person can find strength
time and again♪

526
00:29:57,220 --> 00:29:59,660
♪Our past♪

527
00:30:00,380 --> 00:30:03,340
♪Has been full of ups and downs
along the way♪

528
00:30:04,100 --> 00:30:07,660
♪Admitting my confusion
just like your regret♪

529
00:30:07,660 --> 00:30:10,900
♪How hard can it be?♪

530
00:30:10,950 --> 00:30:12,280
Your knot

531
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:14,150
looks more exquisite
the more I look at it.

532
00:30:15,840 --> 00:30:17,150
I wonder when

533
00:30:18,670 --> 00:30:20,150
I will also be on someone's mind,

534
00:30:21,910 --> 00:30:23,120
and have someone

535
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:25,950
pray for my good fortune and longevity.

536
00:30:25,950 --> 00:30:31,380
♪Stepping out of this long game
of hide-and-seek♪

537
00:30:32,420 --> 00:30:38,420
♪The flustered mortal world♪

538
00:30:39,780 --> 00:30:45,900
♪Your eyes remain clear and bright♪

539
00:31:04,980 --> 00:31:09,420
(East Palace)

540
00:31:15,910 --> 00:31:16,710
I thought

541
00:31:18,360 --> 00:31:19,150
you wouldn't come.

542
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:20,600
Since you invited me,

543
00:31:20,950 --> 00:31:22,080
I would naturally come.

544
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,430
So,

545
00:31:28,990 --> 00:31:30,190
what is your answer?

546
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,080
For that one year,

547
00:31:37,430 --> 00:31:39,280
I'll be a good wife to you.

548
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:49,230
Don't move.

549
00:31:59,990 --> 00:32:00,990
You know very well

550
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:04,670
I'm only marrying you
because you have one year left to live.

551
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:07,080
Yet you're still so happy.

552
00:32:09,540 --> 00:32:11,800
Each dawn, each dusk,
each moment together,

553
00:32:12,670 --> 00:32:13,840
that will be a lifetime.

554
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:16,190
My life

555
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:18,390
rises and sets like the sun.

556
00:32:19,560 --> 00:32:20,320
My heart

557
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,040
remains unchanged for eternity.

558
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:30,640
I chose the nearest auspicious date.

559
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:43,360
(Yong'an Hall)

560
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:44,080
Grandmother,

561
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:45,840
I came to see you as soon as I returned.

562
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:48,430
What a filial child.

563
00:32:48,430 --> 00:32:49,670
How has your health been lately?

564
00:32:49,670 --> 00:32:50,710
Good.

565
00:32:52,360 --> 00:32:53,990
Greetings, Your Highness.

566
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:55,320
You may rise.

567
00:33:03,620 --> 00:33:05,220
Greetings, Commandery Princess.

568
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,280
Greetings, Your Highness.

569
00:33:09,670 --> 00:33:12,120
I asked Xihe to come keep me company.

570
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:14,520
She is about to marry the Crown Prince.

571
00:33:14,520 --> 00:33:15,320
Soon,

572
00:33:15,470 --> 00:33:17,640
she will become your sister-in-law.

573
00:33:24,520 --> 00:33:26,640
I heard you will stay in the capital.

574
00:33:27,230 --> 00:33:27,800
Yes.

575
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,540
Father has issued a decree,

576
00:33:29,560 --> 00:33:31,790
appointing me
as the General of the Gallant Cavalry.

577
00:33:31,800 --> 00:33:33,240
Congratulations, Your Highness.

578
00:33:35,040 --> 00:33:36,120
I always remember

579
00:33:36,990 --> 00:33:38,950
the times I spent with you.

580
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:42,530
Taking care of the children
in Gudu Garden together,

581
00:33:42,530 --> 00:33:45,400
paying respects to the fallen soldiers
at the cemetery together.

582
00:33:46,950 --> 00:33:47,950
Far away in Anlan,

583
00:33:48,150 --> 00:33:49,390
in the dead of night,

584
00:33:49,910 --> 00:33:51,950
I sometimes regretted
leaving the imperial capital.

585
00:33:53,470 --> 00:33:55,280
You are a born soldier.

586
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,040
At that time, the imperial capital

587
00:33:57,090 --> 00:33:59,300
wasn't the best place for you
to showcase your talents.

588
00:33:59,430 --> 00:34:00,800
Your ideals and ambitions

589
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,080
belong on the battlefield.

590
00:34:02,390 --> 00:34:04,390
Defending the country
is beyond reproach.

591
00:34:05,190 --> 00:34:06,360
You made the right choice.

592
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,710
Don't worry.

593
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,280
I didn't come back this time
to pester you.

594
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,280
The past is in the past.

595
00:34:21,230 --> 00:34:22,470
I only wish you

596
00:34:23,230 --> 00:34:24,230
a smooth future

597
00:34:24,750 --> 00:34:25,800
and to follow your heart.

598
00:34:49,560 --> 00:34:50,560
I invited you here today

599
00:34:51,080 --> 00:34:52,600
to pick out your wedding dress.

600
00:34:53,650 --> 00:34:55,030
All the ceremonies for our wedding

601
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:57,710
are handled by the Palace Administration
and various departments,

602
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,760
in coordination
with the Ministry of Ceremonies.

603
00:34:59,950 --> 00:35:02,040
But Xihe, you should
choose what you like.

604
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:03,360
Take your time.

605
00:35:04,640 --> 00:35:06,040
I only hope that on the wedding day,

606
00:35:06,390 --> 00:35:07,880
I can see joy in your eyes.

607
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,840
Thank you for your trouble,
Your Highness.

608
00:35:11,470 --> 00:35:13,430
This booklet follows
the royal regulations

609
00:35:13,430 --> 00:35:14,670
for your wedding attire.

610
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,290
Please take a look, Your Highness.

611
00:35:16,310 --> 00:35:18,320
(Crown Prince's Wedding Attire Catalog)

612
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,320
If I may, Your Highness,

613
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:21,120
royal weddings in our dynasty

614
00:35:21,120 --> 00:35:23,640
favor bright colors,
usually with crimson as the main color,

615
00:35:23,750 --> 00:35:25,360
paired with various patterns.

616
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,080
This white pattern is so unique.

617
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,670
It looks like a sky full of stars.

618
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,320
All the wedding dresses

619
00:35:47,620 --> 00:35:50,680
will be made according to Commandery
Princess Zhaoning's preferences.

620
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:51,920
Yes, Your Highness.

621
00:35:58,700 --> 00:36:05,580
(Auspicious)

622
00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:26,230
Your Highness,

623
00:36:26,640 --> 00:36:28,150
the pearls on this veil

624
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:30,950
were personally selected for you
by the Crown Prince.

625
00:36:31,230 --> 00:36:33,150
And he strung them one by one

626
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:34,470
with his own hands.

627
00:36:34,710 --> 00:36:35,840
This shows

628
00:36:35,910 --> 00:36:38,190
His Highness's sincerity
in marrying you.

629
00:36:44,080 --> 00:36:44,750
Put it on.

630
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:27,830
Her Highness looks like
a fairy descending to earth.

631
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:30,600
Why are you crying on such a joyous day?

632
00:37:38,340 --> 00:37:40,400
The bridal procession
from the East Palace is here!

633
00:38:10,640 --> 00:38:11,960
Please have a seat, you two.

634
00:38:13,790 --> 00:38:14,520
I'm not tired.

635
00:38:19,750 --> 00:38:21,920
The Commandery Princess has arrived.

636
00:39:44,600 --> 00:39:46,000
Bow.

637
00:39:52,710 --> 00:39:54,520
Bow again.

638
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,480
Xihe,

639
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:08,920
your father and brother are not here.

640
00:40:09,310 --> 00:40:12,440
Today, your uncle and I

641
00:40:13,190 --> 00:40:14,710
will see you off to your marriage.

642
00:40:15,270 --> 00:40:16,440
May the two of you

643
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:18,920
be of one mind and heart,

644
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:20,870
respect each other,

645
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:23,120
tie the knot forever,

646
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:26,120
and form a lifelong bond.

647
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:29,750
I wish you

648
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:32,880
mutual respect and harmony
in your marriage.

649
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:34,960
May you live in harmony,

650
00:40:35,790 --> 00:40:37,190
continue the family line,

651
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:40,560
and grow old together.

652
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:43,080
Grandfather and Uncle, I will always

653
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:46,080
keep your earnest teachings in my heart.

654
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:50,310
Don't miss the auspicious hour.

655
00:40:50,830 --> 00:40:51,640
Go.

656
00:40:53,870 --> 00:40:55,600
The bride departs!

657
00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:07,310
Set off.

658
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:29,030
Your Highness, please behave yourself.

659
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:31,480
On our wedding night,
with my beautiful bride,

660
00:42:31,830 --> 00:42:33,150
perhaps you could teach me

661
00:42:33,440 --> 00:42:34,400
how to behave.

662
00:42:34,870 --> 00:42:38,190
Your Highness,
you and Xihe are newlyweds,

663
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:41,080
but you should still
exercise some restraint.

664
00:42:47,031 --> 00:42:49,971
♪I've hidden so many words♪

665
00:42:50,591 --> 00:42:53,391
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

666
00:42:54,261 --> 00:43:01,231
♪So never uncover♪

667
00:43:01,421 --> 00:43:03,781
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

668
00:43:04,911 --> 00:43:07,641
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

669
00:43:08,601 --> 00:43:13,941
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

670
00:43:15,701 --> 00:43:18,521
♪Every answer I gave♪

671
00:43:19,321 --> 00:43:22,171
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

672
00:43:22,961 --> 00:43:26,331
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

673
00:43:26,591 --> 00:43:29,901
♪How hard it truly was?♪

674
00:43:32,871 --> 00:43:36,311
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

675
00:43:37,301 --> 00:43:39,631
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

676
00:43:40,901 --> 00:43:46,661
♪Pretending to be brave
as if I'd never been hurt♪

677
00:43:48,071 --> 00:43:51,201
♪It's a shame I never could♪

678
00:43:51,651 --> 00:43:54,661
♪Give you a moon in return♪

679
00:43:54,771 --> 00:44:01,411
♪With the same open heart you loved me♪

680
00:44:01,411 --> 00:44:05,081
♪I've crossed the wasteland of memories♪

681
00:44:05,951 --> 00:44:08,711
♪Never knowing I was lost♪

682
00:44:09,151 --> 00:44:12,281
♪Why don't you take me away?♪

683
00:44:12,721 --> 00:44:18,671
♪Lead me out of this endless game
of hide-and-seek♪

684
00:44:20,071 --> 00:44:23,621
♪You'll never♪

685
00:44:23,901 --> 00:44:33,371
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

686
00:44:59,541 --> 00:45:03,021
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this film)

